text:
I bought Windows 10 today from Gamecheap way way way way under MS Pro Version. I read some reviews most positive but some negative mostly directed to install. Well I am here to tell you I am fair from being a master of technology but given the price offering by GC it was too good to pass up.
Glad I did and install was seamless and not at all too complex for my abilities.
Thank you Gamecheap
John
